##About Me
Hi!  I'm Matthew Ielusic, and I'm an undergrad Computer Science student at Georgia Tech.  I'm interested in computer science and computer games, and have written a few programs connecting my two hobbies.  I've worked in Java and Haskell, and know a bit of C.  I've written an [add-on of sorts](http://matthew-ielusic.github.io/Minecraft-Gas-Systems-/) for the game Minecraft.

## My Projects
Independently I've written I've written an [add-on of sorts](http://matthew-ielusic.github.io/Minecraft-Gas-Systems-/) and a [data-mining tool](http://matthew-ielusic.github.io/WorldofTanks-DataMining-/) for players of World of Tanks.  As part of my schoolwork I've written a [text adventure game](insert link here).
